        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Because multi line suggestions are computed based on your current line's indentation, and not to scroll makes the indentation wrong, (not copilot but something similar)\n\nhttps://github.com/user-attachments/assets/4ec510be-4529-44f6-a12c-3836251a4fe1\n",
